  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project shall target factors that impact drug use. World Concern will work towards increasing youth resistance to first drug use, child and youth resistance to illegal drugs, villages decreasing their illegal drug use, and Government agencies (private and voluntary) increasing coordination and access to services. Some ways in which this will be carried out is through trainers and peer educators and their work to provide life skills training, alternative recreational activities, awareness training, mobilizing Drug Prevention Teams, and implementing Village Drug Prevention Plans.</narrative>
  </description>
